{"id":232926734,"title":"增肌期","content":"小弟我目前身高體重/肌肉量體脂如下圖\n我有一個問題，我蛋白質攝取體重的兩倍，但我增肌期會用碳循環的方式，這樣真的可以有效增肌嗎？\n還是碳水應該也穩定，蛋白質體重*2剩下給脂肪?\n目前我的體重確實上升變成65kg，但還不到一個月上升了三公斤，是不是哪裡飲食上有問題（高碳日:早餐:吐司、饅頭類，中餐跟晚餐一定一般便當飯量。\n低碳日:早餐有時蛋餅，有時麥片，有時不攝取碳水，中餐就是蔬菜類跟蛋還有肉，晚餐大概全家白飯一半份量。）\n不好意思第一次發文排版有點不好，我主要是對碳水攝取量的問題有疑問，煩請高人指點一下，謝謝🙏🙇‍♂️https://i.imgur.com/2ZFvUm9.jpg","excerpt":"小弟我目前身高體重/肌肉量體脂如下圖，我有一個問題，我蛋白質攝取體重的兩倍，但我增肌期會用碳循環的方式，這樣真的可以有效增肌嗎？還是碳水應該也穩定，蛋白質體重*2剩下給脂肪？目前我的體重確實上升變成6","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"9b5213d6-4427-4a3c-b788-efa19493631c","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-20T13:22:28.980Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-20T13:22:28.980Z","commentCount":13,"likeCount":2,"tags":[],"topics":["健身房","增肌","飲食"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"健身","forumAlias":"fitness","school":"輔仁大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":2}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/2ZFvUm9.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"0e79dd6c-5cc8-4907-8b2e-90200738d0fe","url":"https://i.imgur.com/2ZFvUm9l.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/2ZFvUm9l.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/2ZFvUm9l.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-20T13:22:28.980Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-20T13:22:28.980Z"},{"id":"0e79dd6c-5cc8-4907-8b2e-90200738d0fe","url":"https://i.imgur.com/2ZFvUm9.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/2ZFvUm9","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/2ZFvUm9l.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-20T13:22:28.980Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-20T13:22:28.980Z"}],"postAvatar":""}